<title>ITALY: Italian stock, futures indices hit record highs.</title>
<headline>Italian stock, futures indices hit record highs.</headline>
<dateline>MILAN 1997-06-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Italy's blue-chip Mib30 stock index and the Fib30 bourse futures index both hit record highs in late European trade on Wednesday.</p>
<p>The MIb30 index rose to 19541 before slipping back to stand 1.55 percent up on the day at 19531.</p>
<p>The June contract on the Fib30 index climbed to 19575 and was standing at 19560 at 1433 GMT.</p>
<p>--Milan bureau +39 2 66129507</p>
